Notes: Southwest Baptist rallies from a 10-point deficit (48-38) to pull out a win at
UMR...SBU goes up for good on Jennifer Clymore's three-pointer with 1:23 to
play...UMR's Jamie Forsberg misses a potential game-tying trey at the buzzer.
SBU's Amber Wheeler goes over the 1,000-pt. mark for her career (1,002).
Game.Officials: John Murray,  Tom Sullivan,  Heath Harms
